  \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilot-excel.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilot-excel.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilot-excel.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilot-excel.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1300\" height=\"650\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Copilot side panel in Excel.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilot-excel.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilot-excel.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eEven though the \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/microsoft-365-subscription-with-copilot-price-increase/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eCopilot integration in Microsoft 365 came with a small price increase\u003c/a\u003e, it\u0026#39;s worth it compared to paying for Copilot Pro separately. It can help you create formulas, summarize Pivot Tables and charts, or analyze your data to understand some insights.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eWhile \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/use-google-duet-ai-google-sheets/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGoogle Sheets and its Gemini integration\u003c/a\u003e are free, they\u0026#39;re much more limited than Excel and Copilot. \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/gemini-google-sheets-review-gimmick-or-game-changer/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGemini in Google Sheets feels more like a gimmick\u003c/a\u003e than an actually useful feature.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"excel-is-the-industry-standard\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e5 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Excel Is the Industry Standard\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eExcel has existed since 1985, and Google Sheets since 2006. Because Excel is two decades older, it has a long history and established presence in the business world. It\u0026#39;s a universally recognized tool and is so deeply ingrained in many business workflows that it\u0026#39;s hard to abandon.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eEven organizations that use other software like Tableau might require it to interact with Excel to, for instance, take advantage of its advanced data analysis and reporting capabilities. Excel\u0026#39;s widespread use is also one reason it has many add-ins—the demand for them is high.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"c699-4b7c-94cfe072134a\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/top-excel-formulas-for-office-worker/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/an-excel-spreadsheet-on-a-tablet-on-an-office-desk-with-pens-a-calculator-and-some-papers-around.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/an-excel-spreadsheet-on-a-tablet-on-an-office-desk-with-pens-a-calculator-and-some-papers-around.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/an-excel-spreadsheet-on-a-tablet-on-an-office-desk-with-pens-a-calculator-and-some-papers-around.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/an-excel-spreadsheet-on-a-tablet-on-an-office-desk-with-pens-a-calculator-and-some-papers-around.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/an-excel-spreadsheet-on-a-tablet-on-an-office-desk-with-pens-a-calculator-and-some-papers-around.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/an-excel-spreadsheet-on-a-tablet-on-an-office-desk-with-pens-a-calculator-and-some-papers-around.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/an-excel-spreadsheet-on-a-tablet-on-an-office-desk-with-pens-a-calculator-and-some-papers-around.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/an-excel-spreadsheet-on-a-tablet-on-an-office-desk-with-pens-a-calculator-and-some-papers-around.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/an-excel-spreadsheet-on-a-tablet-on-an-office-desk-with-pens-a-calculator-and-some-papers-around.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"An Excel spreadsheet on a tablet on an office desk with pens, a calculator, and some papers around.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/an-excel-spreadsheet-on-a-tablet-on-an-office-desk-with-pens-a-calculator-and-some-papers-around.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/an-excel-spreadsheet-on-a-tablet-on-an-office-desk-with-pens-a-calculator-and-some-papers-around.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/top-excel-formulas-for-office-worker/\" title=\"The Top 6 Excel Formulas Every Office Worker Should Know\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\tThe Top 6 Excel Formulas Every Office Worker Should Know\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eOnce you learn these formulas, you\u0026#39;ll wonder how you ever worked without them.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"excel-has-more-add-ins\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e6 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Excel Has More Add-Ins\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/add-ins-excel.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/add-ins-excel.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/add-ins-excel.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/add-ins-excel.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/add-ins-excel.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/add-ins-excel.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/add-ins-excel.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/add-ins-excel.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/add-ins-excel.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1250\" height=\"625\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"The Office Add-Ins store in Excel.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/add-ins-excel.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/add-ins-excel.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e Since Excel has been around for much longer than Google Sheets, developers have had more time to develop a wide range of add-ins. With various add-ins, Excel can make you more productive, whether you\u0026#39;re performing complex calculations, analyzing advanced analytics, or creating automations and visualizations. That means if you want added functionality in your spreadsheets, you\u0026#39;re more likely to find it with Excel than with Google Sheets.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eGoogle Sheets has its merits since it\u0026#39;s quite user-friendly, has better real-time collaboration, and is seamlessly integrated with Google Workspace applications. But Excel just brings more to the table when it comes to offline capabilities, performance, advanced features, Copilot integrations, and add-ins.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eWhen you also consider that it is an industry standard that will not be dethroned anytime soon, my choice to return to it was much easier.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
